Start hadoop daemons    :   sbin/start-dfs.sh (while in the $HADOOP_HOME)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Start Yarn daemons      :     sbin/start-yarn.sh (while in the $HADOOP_HOME)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
hdfs dfs                :   identifier for interacting with the file system
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
hdfs dfs -ls            :   list all files in a hadoop directory
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
hdfs dfs -put           :   moves file from Local to hdfs
OR
hdfs dfs -copyFromLocal
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
hdfs dfs -get           :   moves file from hdfs to Local system
OR
hdfs dfs -copyToLocal
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
hdfs fsck               :   checks status of a directory
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
hdfs dfs -touchz        :   creates an empty file